author: Hypebeast (info@hypebeast.com)
title: SZA Previews a New Travis Scott Collaboration
text:
Despite stirring up some controversy towards the end of last year TDE signee SZA's long-awaited debut album is looking like it'll be releasing sometime this year. The 26-year-old performed some new material in front of an intimate crowd in New York City earlier in the week, reaffirming that the project is well worth the wait. Arguably the most intriguing out of all the songs was "Love Galore," which according to Billboard , is said to be a Travis Scott collaboration. You can get a preview of the Travis-featured song below.
